      • sort

        @NotNull
DataSetAccessor sort(@Nullable
                              java.lang.String sort)
        Specify optional Lucene sorting string, for now it is ignored when something else than Lucene query was used by user.

        Format: field ids separated by space and '~' before the field id for descending sorting. Example: "~created ~id"
        Returns:
